reviews.review_text:
very nice I have waited and waited for this show to be released with an audiance. Sure took along long long time.  Have been to many many shows over the years. With many stand outs. This was just another one of those nights.......   There were times they put us back on our heels. This being one of them. To me that is.  Sound is good usual Kaiser sound. God I loved that place just had everything we wanted and or needed... How many east coast venues had a bar in them? Not that that was the selling point just another quality to add to the mix.  Plus am a big fan of laid back crowds not the hyped up crowd going nuts type.
 So here is why it was a high point in my life. Music wise that is. They bust out the big boy pete. Play the shakedown at breakdown spead. As I remember was hard to keep up dancing at that pace.. To me any show they do the full playin in band is a hot show with maybe the exception of 7 or 10 of them I had been to. She belongs to me was always a favorite of mine, am glad they played it this year only. With the exception of so many years ago that is.  Other One wharf rat palyin Gimme Gimme midnight Hour    Walking the dog.  are you kidding me.If they played like this every night there would have been double  the touch heads years later  THANK GOD THEY DIDN'T.   It's shows like this kept us coming year after year show after show.  Always wating for the block buster show to say OMG they blew the doors off the place tonight huh?  4 stars cause have not listen to complete show as of yet. maybe am wrong for comenting with the heart not the ears.
fantastic sounds  great sound quality and a hot performance.  what a great night.
